column4: Can someone help me with Ubuntu 11.04 and HP Deskjet 1020? It won't print out anything anymore.

it is attached to my machine
first try to update the machine.  that's always first step in something not working, then from there we will continue

would there be any difference regarding OS version ? I could try
yes, because of the software asked to install would be outdated and ubuntu has changed alot since feisty
